### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Decisions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/decisions

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Model providers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/model-providers

### Model profiles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/model-profiles

### ima Skill status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ima-skill

### Bind ima Skill
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ima-skill/bind
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "replace-with-your-ima-skill-key",
  "boundAccount": "your-ima-account"
}

### Knowledge scopes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge-scopes

### Create project
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "自然资源一张图智能化升级方案",
  "customerName": "某市自然资源局",
  "industry": "自然资源",
  "customerType": "政府",
  "background": "客户希望整合现有 GIS 平台、业务系统和数据资源。",
  "rawDemand": "支持二三维一体化展示、专题图层管理、空间分析和业务审批联动。",
  "existingSystems": "已有基础 GIS 平台、不动产登记系统、规划审批系统。",
  "budget": "暂未明确",
  "deliveryTime": "8 周初稿",
  "knowledgeScopeIds": [],
  "deliverables": ["WORD", "PPT", "ARCHITECTURE"]
}

### Projects
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects

### Run requirement agent
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{{projectId}}/agents/requirement/run

### Test ima search
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ima-skill/test-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "iPortal 资源授权能力"
}
